des:
With the official PRESIDENTIAL RADIO Skill, you can hear your favorite radio right now on Alexa! 

PRESIDENTIAL is a global online radio station, bringing people closer to artists and fans through unique music experiences and the highest sound quality of a varied mix of all your favorite music from around the world.

With Alexa Routines you can automatically open the radio skill every morning and listen to PRESIDENTIAL RADIO!
